data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful country setting! This affordable 3 bedroom/2 bath home sits on 10.4 acres of secluded land, on a dead end street, in the desirable South Beauregard School district. Snuggle up to a cozy fire at the fire-pit and toast some s’mores! Property is complete with 2 storage sheds for your outdoor equipment storage needs. Seller is willing to negotiate any required repairs required for FHA or VA loans. Home is located in flood zone X where flood insurance is typically not required. Call your agent today for your personal tour.
